{
  "stem": "7358.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The German.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He used to come-- he used to surprise the people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody ever knew when he would show up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when he came, he always managed to find a victim.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Either he-- he-- he humiliated people by lashing-- beating a person with a whip-- in front of all the workers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And on one occasion, as I mentioned before, he had killed a person not too far from myself.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There's been another incident where he had found some objection about some-- somebody's work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he-- he-- he took out his pistol, and he shot-- and he was about to shoot the man in his head, and the pistol did not fire.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he-- he aimed-- he aimed again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And twice, the pistol did not fire.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he said to the man, you see-- you seem to be some kind of a devil.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I guess you are destined to live.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he let him go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So but this is horrified all the people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just a frightening scene.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know my-- my mother used to-- before my sister used to go to work with me, my mother would take some black ashes and-- and-- and-- and make her-- and dress her in such a way to look ugly so she wouldn't be noticed and-- and-- and raped by-- because-- by the commisar-- by the Russ-- by the German commissar.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He used to-- when he noticed a good looking girl that he liked, he would call over the foreman and-- and just point this girl out to him and say that whatever time, like tomorrow night at such and such time, this girl is to be brought to my house.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and all the women lived in constant fear that they would be selected by him.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
